<LegalLayout title="USDA Non-Discrimination Statement">
  <p>
    MAS MN does not discriminate on the basis of race, color, national origin, religion, sex,
    disability, age, marital or family status, income derived from public assistance, political
    beliefs, or prior civil rights activity in any of its programs or activities, including those
    funded in whole or part by the U.S. Department of Agriculture (USDA).
  </p>
  <p>
    Questions about this statement or MAS Minnesota's food shelf and social services programs can
    be directed to <a href="mailto:info@masmn.org">info@masmn.org</a> or
    <a href="tel:+16514577170">(651) 457-7170</a>.
  </p>
